j/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/architecture/session-routing.md:\n  Line 80: | Cookie | `agentcube_session` | Browser-based clients |\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/architecture/components.md:\n  Line 54: - Watches multiple CRD types in the `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API group\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/getting-started/configuration.md:\n  Line 27: | `router.image.repository` | Router container image | `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router` |\n  Line 32: | `router.sessionStore.url` | Redis/Valkey connection URL | `redis://agentcube-redis:6379` |\n  Line 39: | `workloadManager.image.repository` | Container image | `ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-workloadmanager` |\n  Line 42: | `workloadManager.sandboxNamespace` | Default namespace for sandboxes | `agentcube-sandboxes` |\n  Line 82:   name: agentcube-config\n  Line 83:   namespace: agentcube-system\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/getting-started/quick-start.md:\n  Line 21: kubectl get pods -n agentcube-system\n  Line 32: apiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\n  Line 60: export ROUTER_URL=$(kubectl get svc -n agentcube-system agentcube-router -o jsonpath='{.spec.clusterIP}')\n  Line 87: from agentcube import AgentCubeClient\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/getting-started/installation.md:\n  Line 26: helm repo add agentcube https://volcano-sh.github.io/agentcube/charts\n  Line 33: kubectl create namespace agentcube-system\n  Line 39: helm install agentcube agentcube/agentcube \\\n  Line 40:   --namespace agentcube-system \\\n  Line 47: kubectl get pods -n agentcube-system\n  Line 54: agentcube-router-xxxxxxxxxx-xxxxx   1/1     Running   0          2m\n  Line 55: agentcube-workloadmanager-xxxx-xx   1/1     Running   0          2m\n  Line 56: agentcube-redis-xxxxxxxxxx-xxxxx    1/1     Running   0          2m\n  Line 111: helm install agentcube agentcube/agentcube \\\n  Line 112:   --namespace agentcube-system \\\n  Line 130: helm uninstall agentcube --namespace agentcube-system\n  Line 131: kubectl delete namespace agentcube-system\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/intro.md:\n  Line 5: keywords: [agentcube, kubernetes, sandbox, ai-agents, orchestration]\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/src/pages/index.module.css:\n  Line 6:   background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ifm-color-primary) 0%, var(--agentcube-accent) 100%);\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/src/css/custom.css:\n  Line 21:   --agentcube-accent: #4a90d9;\n  Line 22:   --agentcube-accent-dark: #357abd;\n  Line 23:   --agentcube-success: #2e8555;\n  Line 24:   --agentcube-warning: #f0ad4e;\n  Line 25:   --agentcube-danger: #d9534f;\n  Line 26:   --agentcube-info: #5bc0de;\n  Line 39:   --agentcube-accent: #5ba0e9;\n\n(Results truncated: showing 100 of 2401 matches (2301 hidden). Consider using a more specific path or pattern.)","metadata":{"matches":2401,"truncated":true},"title":"agentcube","time":{"start":1775901679073,"end":1775901679095}}}}
