{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775901684563,"sessionID":"ses_28402f884ffeKORgYfcWyIxWRs","part":{"id":"prt_d7bfd2f45001USWu3a3xMkLk0E","messageID":"msg_d7bfd1e720015QEG9u7CMlx16J","sessionID":"ses_28402f884ffeKORgYfcWyIxWRs","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_df18af17cd32430789608ee4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-043"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-043</path>\n<type>directory</type>\n<entries>\ndelta-spec.md\ndesign.md\nproposal.md\ntasks.md\n\n(4 entries)\n</entries>","metadata":{"preview":"delta-spec.md\ndesign.md\nproposal.md\ntasks.md","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-043","time":{"start":1775901684548,"end":1775901684562}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775901685961,"sessionID":"ses_28402f884ffeKORgYfcWyIxWRs","part":{"id":"prt_d7bfd33da001U6KM8vI4KGEUvt","messageID":"msg_d7bfd1e720015QEG9u7CMlx16J","sessionID":"ses_28402f884ffeKORgYfcWyIxWRs","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_925cacb34ddc43e7921cb4f2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-043/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-043/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-043: 架构设计文档与 API 文档 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Context\n4: \n5: - **Module:** `docs/`\n6: - **Language:** Markdown (Docusaurus 3.x)\n7: - **Size:** M\n8: - **Base specs:** `docs/docs/architecture/overview.md`, `docs/docs/architecture/components.md`, `docs/sidebars.ts`\n9: \n10: ## Scope\n11: \n12: This delta spec defines the requirements for completing the AgentCube documentation site. The Docusaurus 3.x site scaffolding exists with sidebar navigation defined, but several documentation sections are empty or missing. This spec covers the creation of API Reference, Architecture, Integrations, Operations, and Contributing documentation, plus quality standards for all docs.\n13: \n14: ---\n15: \n16: ## R-1: Control Plane API Reference\n17: \n18: **Scope:** `docs/docs/api-reference/control-plane.md` — WorkloadManager REST API endpoints\n19: \n20: ### Requirement: WorkloadManager API 文档完整性\n21: \n22: The Control Plane API reference SHALL document all WorkloadManager REST endpoints with request/response schemas.\n23: \n24: #### Scenario: Sandbox 创建接口文档\n25: \n26: - **GIVEN** `docs/docs/api-reference/control-plane.md` 已创建\n27: - **WHEN** 读者查看 Sandbox 创建接口文档\n28: - **THEN** 文档包含 `POST /api/v1/sandboxes` 的完整说明\n29:   AND 请求体 schema 包含 `kind`（\"AgentRuntime\" | \"CodeInterpreter\"）、`name`、`namespace`、`metadata`、`ttl` 字段\n30:   AND 响应体 schema 包含 `sessionId`、`sandboxId`、`sandboxName`、`entryPoints` 字段\n31:   AND 成功响应状态码为 201\n32:   AND 错误响应包含 400（校验失败）、404（模板不存在）、500（内部错误）\n33: \n34: #### Scenario: Sandbox 查询接口文档\n35: \n36: - **GIVEN** Control Plane API 文档已创建\n37: - **WHEN** 读者查看 Sandbox 查询接口\n38: - **THEN** 文档包含 `GET /api/v1/sandboxes/:sessionID` 的说明\n39:   AND 路径参数 `sessionID` 已描述\n40:   AND 响应体包含 sandbox 状态信息\n41:   AND 文档包含 `GET /api/v1/sandboxes` 列表接口说明\n42:   AND 列表接口支持 `?namespace=` 和 `?status=` 查询参数\n43: \n44: #### Scenario: Sandbox 删除接口文档\n45: \n46: - **GIVEN** Control Plane API 文档已创建\n47: - **WHEN** 读者查看 Sandbox 删除接口\n48: - **THEN** 文档包含 `DELETE /api/v1/sandboxes/:sessionID` 的说明\n49:   AND 描述了幂等删除行为（404 视为成功）\n50:   AND 响应状态码包含 200（成功）、404（不存在）、500（内部错误）\n51: \n52: #### Scenario: Sandbox TTL 延长接口文档\n53: \n54: - **GIVEN** Control Plane API 文档已创建\n55: - **WHEN** 读者查看 TTL 延长接口\n56: - **THEN** 文档包含 `POST /api/v1/sandboxes/:sessionID/extend` 的说明\n57:   AND 请求体 schema 包含 `extensionDuration` 字段\n58:   AND 描述了 TTL 延长对 sandbox 生命周期的影响\n59: \n60: #### Scenario: 健康检查接口文档\n61: \n62: - **GIVEN** Control Plane API 文档已创建\n63: - **WHEN** 读者查看健康检查接口\n64: - **THEN** 文档包含 `GET /health/live`（liveness probe）的说明\n65:   AND 文档包含 `GET /health/ready`（readiness probe）的说明\n66:   AND 两个接口均返回 `{\"status\": \"ok\"}`\n67: \n68: ### Requirement: API 文档使用 ApiEndpoint MDX 组件\n69: \n70: #### Scenario: 接口文档使用标准化组件\n71: \n72: - **GIVEN** `docs/src/components/ApiEndpoint/` 组件已存在\n73: - **WHEN** Control Plane API 文档编写接口说明\n74: - **THEN** 每个接口使用 `<ApiEndpoint>` MDX 组件展示\n75:   AND 组件包含 method（GET/POST/DELETE）、path、description 属性\n76:   AND 请求/响应示例使用代码块展示\n77: \n78: ---\n79: \n80: ## R-2: Data Plane API Reference\n81: \n82: **Scope:** `docs/docs/api-reference/data-plane.md` — Router proxy endpoints + PicoD API\n83: \n84: ### Requirement: Router 代理接口文档完整性\n85: \n86: The Data Plane API reference SHALL document all Router proxy endpoints.\n87: \n88: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 调用接口文档\n89: \n90: - **GIVEN** `docs/docs/api-reference/data-plane.md` 已创建\n91: - **WHEN** 读者查看 AgentRuntime 调用接口\n92: - **THEN** 文档包含 `GET/POST /v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path` 的说明\n93:   AND 描述了 Router 作为反向代理的行为\n94:   AND 响应头 `x-agentcube-session-id` 的用途已说明\n95:   AND 描述了 session 自动创建流程（首次请求时）\n96: \n97: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter 调用接口文档\n98: \n99: - **GIVEN** Data Plane API 文档已创建\n100: - **WHEN** 读者查看 CodeInterpreter 调用接口\n101: - **THEN** 文档包含 `GET/POST /v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path` 的说明\n102:   AND 描述了与 AgentRuntime 调用接口的区别\n103:   AND 路径参数 `namespace`、`name` 和 wildcard `*path` 均已说明\n104: \n105: #### Scenario: Router 健康检查接口文档\n106: \n107: - **GIVEN** Data Plane API 文档已创建\n108: - **WHEN** 读者查看 Router 健康检查\n109: - **THEN** 文档包含 `GET /health/live` 返回 `{\"status\": \"alive\"}` 的说明\n110:   AND 文档包含 `GET /health/ready` 的说明（检查 session manager 可用性）\n111: \n112: ### Requirement: PicoD API 文档完整性\n113: \n114: The Data Plane API reference SHALL document all PicoD internal API endpoints.\n115: \n116: #### Scenario: PicoD 代码执行接口文档\n117: \n118: - **GIVEN** Data Plane API 文档已创建\n119: - **WHEN** 读者查看 PicoD 代码执行接口\n120: - **THEN** 文档包含 `POST /api/execute` 的说明\n121:   AND 请求体 schema 包含 `command`（数组）、`timeout`（字符串如 \"30s\"）、`working_dir`、`env` 字段\n122:   AND 响应体包含执行输出、退出码、错误信息\n123:   AND 描述了 JWT public-key 认证机制\n124: \n125: #### Scenario: PicoD 文件操作接口文档\n126: \n127: - **GIVEN** Data Plane API 文档已创建\n128: - **WHEN** 读者查看 PicoD 文件操作接口\n129: - **THEN** 文档包含 `POST /api/files`（上传，支持 multipart/form-data 和 JSON base64）的说明\n130:   AND 文档包含 `GET /api/files`（目录列表，查询参数 `?path=...`）的说明\n131:   AND 文档包含 `GET /api/files/*path`（文件下载/流式传输）的说明\n132:   AND 文档包含 `GET /health`（返回 service name、version、uptime）的说明\n133: \n134: ---\n135: \n136: ## R-3: CRD Reference\n137: \n138: **Scope:** `docs/docs/api-reference/crds.md` — Kubernetes Custom Resource Definitions\n139: \n140: ### Requirement: AgentRuntime CRD 文档完整性\n141: \n142: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime CR 字段文档\n143: \n144: - **GIVEN** `docs/docs/api-reference/crds.md` 已创建\n145: - **WHEN** 读者查看 AgentRuntime CRD 文档\n146: - **THEN** 文档包含 API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` 的说明\n147:   AND 文档包含 Kind `AgentRuntime` 的完整 spec 字段表：\n148:     - `targetPort[]`（name, port, protocol, pathPrefix）\n149:     - `podTemplate`（SandboxTemplate: labels, annotations, corev1.PodSpec）\n150:     - `sessionTimeout`（空闲超时时长）\n151:     - `maxSessionDuration`（最大会话时长，默认 8h）\n152:   AND 文档包含 status 字段说明（`conditions[]` 标准 metav1.Condition 数组）\n153:   AND 文档包含 YAML 示例\n154: \n155: ### Requirement: CodeInterpreter CRD 文档完整性\n156: \n157: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter CR 字段文档\n158: \n159: - **GIVEN** CRD 文档已创建\n160: - **WHEN** 读者查看 CodeInterpreter CRD 文档\n161: - **THEN** 文档包含 Kind `CodeInterpreter` 的完整 spec 字段表：\n162:     - `ports[]`（TargetPort 列表）\n163:     - `template`（CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate: labels, annotations, runtimeClassName, image, imagePullPolicy, imagePullSecrets, env, command, args, resources）\n164:     - `sessionTimeout`\n165:     - `maxSessionDuration`（默认 8h）\n166:     - `warmPoolSize`（预预热 sandbox 池大小，int32）\n167:     - `authMode`（\"picod\" | \"none\"，默认 \"picod\"）\n168:   AND 文档包含 status 字段说明（`conditions[]`、`ready` 布尔值）\n169:   AND 文档包含 YAML 示例\n170:   AND 文档说明了 warm pool 的工作机制\n171: \n172: ### Requirement: Sandbox 和 SandboxClaim CRD 文档完整性\n173: \n174: #### Scenario: Sandbox CR 字段文档\n175: \n176: - **GIVEN** CRD 文档已创建\n177: - **WHEN** 读者查看 Sandbox CRD 文档\n178: - **THEN** 文档包含 API group `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1` 的说明\n179:   AND 文档包含 Kind `Sandbox` 的 spec 字段（`image`、`command`）和 status 字段（`phase`）\n180:   AND 文档包含 Kind `SandboxClaim`（API group `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`）的说明\n181:   AND 文档说明了 SandboxClaim 与 warm pool 的关系\n182: \n183: ### Requirement: CRD 文档使用 K8sResource MDX 组件\n184: \n185: #### Scenario: CRD 文档使用标准化组件\n186: \n187: - **GIVEN** `docs/src/components/K8sResource/` 组件已存在\n188: - **WHEN** CRD 文档编写资源说明\n189: - **THEN** 使用 `<K8sResource>` MDX 组件展示 CRD 元数据\n190:   AND 组件包含 group、version、kind、scope 属性\n191:   AND 字段定义使用表格展示\n192: \n193: ---\n194: \n195: ## R-4: Architecture Documentation Completeness\n196: \n197: **Scope:** `docs/docs/architecture/` — 补充缺失的架构文档\n198: \n199: ### Requirement: 现有架构文档质量\n200: \n201: #### Scenario: Architecture Overview 完整性\n202: \n203: - **GIVEN** `docs/docs/architecture/overview.md` 已存在\n204: - **WHEN** 读者查看架构概览\n205: - **THEN** 文档包含系统架构图（ASCII 或 Mermaid）\n206:   AND 文档包含设计原则列表\n207:   AND 文档包含组件汇总表\n208:   AND 文档包含数据流说明（6 步流程）\n209:   AND 文档包含指向子文档的导航链接\n210: \n211: #### Scenario: Components 文档完整性\n212: \n213: - **GIVEN** `docs/docs/architecture/components.md` 已存在\n214: - **WHEN** 读者查看组件文档\n215: - **THEN** 文档覆盖所有 5 个核心组件：Router、WorkloadManager、PicoD、Agentd、Session Store\n216:   AND 每个组件包含 Responsibilities、Technical Details 两个子节\n217:   AND WorkloadManager 包含 Reconciliation Loop 说明\n218:   AND Session Store 包含 Data Model 说明（key-value 结构）\n219: \n220: ### Requirement: Session Routing 文档\n221: \n222: #### Scenario: Session Routing 机制文档\n223: \n224: - **GIVEN** `docs/docs/architecture/session-routing.md` 已存在\n225: - **WHEN** 读者查看 session 路由文档\n226: - **THEN** 文档描述了 session 创建、查找、转发的完整流程\n227:   AND 文档描述了 Redis/Valkey 中的 session 数据结构\n228:   AND 文档描述了 session 缓存策略\n229:   AND 文档描述了 JWT 认证在路由中的注入机制\n230: \n231: ### Requirement: Sandbox Lifecycle 文档\n232: \n233: #### Scenario: Sandbox 生命周期文档\n234: \n235: - **GIVEN** `docs/docs/architecture/sandbox-lifecycle.md` 已存在\n236: - **WHEN** 读者查看 sandbox 生命周期文档\n237: - **THEN** 文档描述了 sandbox 的完整生命周期状态机（创建 → 运行 → 空闲 → 清理）\n238:   AND 文档描述了 Agentd 空闲清理机制（默认 30 分钟超时、5 分钟检查间隔）\n239:   AND 文档描述了 graceful shutdown 和 drain period\n240:   AND 文档描述了 warm pool 的生命周期差异\n241: \n242: ---\n243: \n244: ## R-5: Integration Documentation\n245: \n246: **Scope:** `docs/docs/integrations/` — 第三方集成文档\n247: \n248: ### Requirement: Dify Plugin 集成文档\n249: \n250: #### Scenario: Dify Plugin 文档\n251: \n252: - **GIVEN** `docs/docs/integrations/dify-plugin.md` 已创建\n253: - **WHEN** 读者查看 Dify 集成文档\n254: - **THEN** 文档描述了 Dify plugin 的安装步骤\n255:   AND 文档描述了 Dify 与 AgentCube 的对接配置\n256:   AND 文档包含配置示例\n257:   AND 文档描述了 `integrations/` 目录中的 plugin 代码结构\n258: \n259: ### Requirement: LangChain 集成文档\n260: \n261: #### Scenario: LangChain 集成文档\n262: \n263: - **GIVEN** `docs/docs/integrations/langchain.md` 已创建\n264: - **WHEN** 读者查看 LangChain 集成文档\n265: - **THEN** 文档描述了 LangChain tool/agent 与 AgentCube 的集成方式\n266:   AND 文档包含 Python 代码示例\n267:   AND 文档描述了 `AgentRuntimeClient` 在 LangChain 中的使用方式\n268: \n269: ---\n270: \n271: ## R-6: Operations Documentation\n272: \n273: **Scope:** `docs/docs/operations/` — 运维文档\n274: \n275: ### Requirement: Deployment 文档\n276: \n277: #### Scenario: 部署文档\n278: \n279: - **GIVEN** `docs/docs/operations/deployment.md` 已创建\n280: - **WHEN** 读者查看部署文档\n281: - **THEN** 文档描述了 Helm chart 部署方式\n282:   AND 文档描述了 `deployment/` 目录中的 manifests 结构\n283:   AND 文档包含 Docker 多阶段构建说明\n284:   AND 文档包含 GitHub Actions CI/CD 流程说明\n285:   AND 文档包含多 namespace 部署指南\n286: \n287: ### Requirement: Monitoring 文档\n288: \n289: #### Scenario: 监控文档\n290: \n291: - **GIVEN** `docs/docs/operations/monitoring.md` 已创建\n292: - **WHEN** 读者查看监控文档\n293: - **THEN** 文档描述了可用的 metrics（如 WorkloadManager 的 reconciler metrics）\n294:   AND 文档描述了日志采集方式\n295:   AND 文档包含告警规则建议\n296: \n297: ### Requirement: Troubleshooting 文档\n298: \n299: #### Scenario: 故障排查文档\n300: \n301: - **GIVEN** `docs/docs/operations/troubleshooting.md` 已创建\n302: - **WHEN** 读者查看故障排查文档\n303: - **THEN** 文档包含常见问题及解决方案列表\n304:   AND 文档描述了日志查看方法\n305:   AND 文档描述了 session 状态诊断方法\n306: \n307: ### Requirement: Security 文档\n308: \n309: #### Scenario: 安全文档\n310: \n311: - **GIVEN** `docs/docs/operations/security.md` 已创建\n312: - **WHEN** 读者查看安全文档\n313: - **THEN** 文档描述了 JWT RS256 认证机制\n314:   AND 文档描述了 K8s TokenReview 集成\n315:   AND 文档描述了 sandbox 隔离机制（cgroups、namespaces）\n316:   AND 文档描述了 PicoD 的 JWT public-key 认证\n317:   AND 文档描述了网络安全策略建议\n318: \n319: ---\n320: \n321: ## R-7: Contributing Documentation\n322: \n323: **Scope:** `docs/docs/contributing/` — 贡献者指南\n324: \n325: ### Requirement: Development 文档\n326: \n327: #### Scenario: 开发环境搭建文档\n328: \n329: - **GIVEN** `docs/docs/contributing/development.md` 已创建\n330: - **WHEN** 读者查看开发指南\n331: - **THEN** 文档描述了本地开发环境搭建步骤\n332:   AND 文档描述了 Go 和 Python 开发环境要求\n333:   AND 文档描述了 Makefile 常用命令\n334:   AND 文档描述了代码生成流程（hack/ 目录）\n335: \n336: ### Requirement: Testing 文档\n337: \n338: #### Scenario: 测试指南文档\n339: \n340: - **GIVEN** `docs/docs/contributing/testing.md` 已创建\n341: - **WHEN** 读者查看测试指南\n342: - **THEN** 文档描述了 Go 单元测试运行方式\n343:   AND 文档描述了 Python 测试运行方式\n344:   AND 文档描述了 TDD 流程和 `test_spec.md` 约定\n345:   AND 文档描述了测试覆盖率要求\n346: \n347: ### Requirement: Release Process 文档\n348: \n349: #### Scenario: 发布流程文档\n350: \n351: - **GIVEN** `docs/docs/contributing/release-process.md` 已创建\n352: - **WHEN** 读者查看发布流程\n353: - **THEN** 文档描述了语义化版本（semver）策略\n354:   AND 文档描述了 CI/CD 发布流程\n355:   AND 文档描述了 Helm chart 发布流程\n356:   AND 文档描述了文档站点发布流程\n357: \n358: ---\n359: \n360: ## R-8: Documentation Quality Standards\n361: \n362: **Scope:** 全局 — 文档质量标准与 MDX 组件\n363: \n364: ### Requirement: Frontmatter 规范\n365: \n366: #### Scenario: 所有文档包含正确的 frontmatter\n367: \n368: - **GIVEN** 新文档被创建\n369: - **WHEN** 文档被提交\n370: - **THEN** 文档顶部包含 YAML frontmatter\n371:   AND frontmatter 包含 `sidebar_position`（数字）\n372:   AND frontmatter 包含 `title`（字符串）\n373:   AND frontmatter 包含 `description`（字符串，用于 SEO）\n374:   AND frontmatter 包含 `keywords`（字符串数组）\n375: \n376: ### Requirement: MDX 组件使用规范\n377: \n378: #### Scenario: ApiEndpoint 组件正确渲染\n379: \n380: - **GIVEN** `docs/src/components/ApiEndpoint/` 组件存在\n381: - **WHEN** API 文档中使用 `<ApiEndpoint>` 组件\n382: - **THEN** 组件在 Docusaurus 构建中正确渲染\n383:   AND 组件展示 HTTP method 颜色标签\n384:   AND 组件展示 endpoint 路径\n385: \n386: #### Scenario: K8sResource 组件正确渲染\n387: \n388: - **GIVEN** `docs/src/components/K8sResource/` 组件存在\n389: - **WHEN** CRD 文档中使用 `<K8sResource>` 组件\n390: - **THEN** 组件在 Docusaurus 构建中正确渲染\n391:   AND 组件展示 CRD 元数据（group、version、kind、scope）\n392: \n393: ### Requirement: 代码示例规范\n394: \n395: #### Scenario: 代码块包含正确的语言标签\n396: \n397: - **GIVEN** 文档中包含代码示例\n398: - **WHEN** 代码块被渲染\n399: - **THEN** Go 代码使用 `go` 语言标签\n400:   AND Python 代码使用 `python` 语言标签\n401:   AND YAML 使用 `yaml` 语言标签\n402:   AND JSON 使用 `json` 语言标签\n403:   AND Shell 命令使用 `bash` 语言标签\n404:   AND Kubernetes 资源使用 `kubernetes` 语言标签\n405: \n406: ### Requirement: 内部链接有效性\n407: \n408: #### Scenario: 文档间交叉链接有效\n409: \n410: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus 配置 `onBrokenLinks: 'throw'`\n411: - **WHEN** 文档构建执行\n412: - **THEN** 所有内部相对链接指向存在的文件\n413:   AND 所有 sidebar 引用的文档 ID 存在\n414:   AND 不存在 404 链接\n415: \n416: ---\n417: \n418: ## R-9: i18n / Chinese Translation Support\n419: \n420: **Scope:** `docs/i18n/` — 中文翻译框架\n421: \n422: ### Requirement: 中文翻译基础设施\n423: \n424: #### Scenario: 中文翻译目录结构\n425: \n426: - **GIVEN** Docusaurus 配置包含 `locales: ['en', 'zh']`\n427: - **WHEN** 中文翻译文件被添加\n428: - **THEN** 翻译文件位于 `docs/i18n/zh/docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/current/`\n429:   AND 翻译文件路径与英文原文一一对应\n430:   AND 翻译文件包含正确的 frontmatter（中文 title 和 description）\n431: \n432: #### Scenario: 语言切换功能\n433: \n434: - **GIVEN** 导航栏配置了 `localeDropdown`\n435: - **WHEN** 用户在文档站点切换语言\n436: - **THEN** 语言切换器显示 \"English\" 和 \"简体中文\" 选项\n437:   AND 切换后导航至对应语言的相同页面\n438:   AND 未翻译的页面 fallback 到英文原文\n439: \n440: ---\n441: \n442: ## File Structure\n443: \n444: | Path | Role |\n445: |------|------|\n446: | `docs/docs/api-reference/control-plane.md` | **NEW** — WorkloadManager REST API reference |\n447: | `docs/docs/api-reference/data-plane.md` | **NEW** — Router proxy + PicoD API reference |\n448: | `docs/docs/api-reference/crds.md` | **NEW** — Kubernetes CRD reference |\n449: | `docs/docs/integrations/dify-plugin.md` | **NEW** — Dify plugin integration guide |\n450: | `docs/docs/integrations/langchain.md` | **NEW** — LangChain integration guide |\n451: | `docs/docs/operations/deployment.md` | **NEW** — Deployment and CI/CD guide |\n452: | `docs/docs/operations/monitoring.md` | **NEW** — Monitoring and observability |\n453: | `docs/docs/operations/troubleshooting.md` | **NEW** — Troubleshooting guide |\n454: | `docs/docs/operations/security.md` | **NEW** — Security guide |\n455: | `docs/docs/contributing/development.md` | **NEW** — Development environment setup |\n456: | `docs/docs/contributing/testing.md` | **NEW** — Testing guide |\n457: | `docs/docs/contributing/release-process.md` | **NEW** — Release process |\n458: | `docs/docs/user-guide/python-sdk.md` | **NEW** — Python SDK user guide |\n459: | `docs/i18n/zh/` | **NEW** — Chinese translation directory (skeleton) |\n460: | `docs/src/components/ApiEndpoint/` | **已有** — MDX component for API docs |\n461: | `docs/src/components/K8sResource/` | **已有** — MDX component for CRD docs |\n462: | `docs/sidebars.ts` | **已有** — Sidebar navigation config |\n463: | `docs/docusaurus.config.ts` | **已有** — Docusaurus site config |\n464: \n465: ## Dependencies\n466: \n467: - `@docusaurus/preset-classic` — Docusaurus docs preset (已有)\n468: - `@easyops-cn/docusaurus-search-local` — Local search plugin (已有)\n469: - `@docusaurus/theme-mermaid` — Mermaid diagram support (已有)\n470: - `prism-react-renderer` — Code syntax highlighting (已有)\n471: \n472: ## Status\n473: \n474: - [ ] Spec review\n475: - [ ] Implementation\n476: - [ ] Verification\n\n(End of file - total 476 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-043: 架构设计文档与 API 文档 — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** `docs/`\n- **Language:** Markdown (Docusaurus 3.x)\n- **Size:** M\n- **Base specs:** `docs/docs/architecture/overview.md`, `docs/docs/architecture/components.md`, `docs/sidebars.ts`\n\n## Scope\n\nThis delta spec defines the requirements for completing the AgentCube documentation site. The Docusaurus 3.x site scaffolding exists with sidebar navigation defined, but several documentation sections are empty or missing. This spec covers the creation of API Reference, Architecture, Integrations, Operations, and Contributing documentation, plus quality standards for all docs.\n\